snippet.title: JAES Company
snippet.description:
Welcome to our Youtube Learning Channel.
A decade in industrial supplies and technical consultancy has led us to create a worldwide network in sectors such as: MECHANICS, ELECTRONICS and HYDRAULICS.
Today we want to share with you our knowledge about the industrial sector. In this channel you can easily find:

- The videos of every single spare part
- The animated explanation of a wide variety of industrial components
- The DIY videos of some of the most interesting devices

Our GOAL is to RAISE KNOWLEDGE and AWARENESS about the INDUSTRIAL SECTOR.

If you want to collaborate with, you can send us an mail: sales@jaescompany.com
Our website is: https://jaescompany.com/
